import React, { Component, Fragment } from 'react'

export default class SignUp extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Fragment>
        <form>
          <label> Name:
            <input type="text" name="name" />
          </label>
          <label> Email:
            <input type="text" name="email" />
          </label>
          <label> Password:
            <input type="text" name="password" />
          </label>
          <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
        </form>
      </Fragment>
    )
  }
}
